snippet.title: ESF: Final - Goku's Improved Transformation with lightning/thunder Effects (QHD)
snippet.description:
Video is part of: "YES.. WE ARE STILL ALIVE  NEWS!" at:  https://forum.esforces.com/threads/yes-we-are-still-alive.158687

Goku's first transformation has lightning added into the background, with some lovely thunder sounds. It gives an idea how it might look like upon release.
